tool_description: API for US Presidential Election results, by state (from 1976-) and county (eventually, from 2000-)
name: US Presidential Election
title: US Presidential Election

api_list.name: osay
api_list.description: Returns JSON block of results for One State, All Years (OSAY), for the specified US Presidential Election year (i.e., Illinois).

api_list.name: osoy
api_list.description: Returns JSON block of results for One State, One Year (OSOY), for the specified US Presidential Election year (i.e., Illinois/2008).

required_parameters.name: state
required_parameters.description: State Name or Abbreviation. Use spaces for multi-word states (i.e., New York)

api_list.name: asoy
api_list.description: Returns JSON block of results for All States, One Year (ASOY), for the specified US Presidential Election year (i.e., 2008).

required_parameters.name: year
required_parameters.description: Election year. Can be either a string or a number type.
